{"tid":402173,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"廢青廢到紐西蘭，瘋狂食牛扒之旅","createTime":"2017-09-16T08:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T13:54:05.000Z","uid":632,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fafabb3e0ea51e7e8d833940d9e8f26d4ad3473e","tid":402173,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"背景：<br />\n續三月份去完Cambodia, 身為窮學生既我見到有紐西蘭既平機票，HX來回2人共6000大元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。所以就同廢青女友定左8月尾去到9月頭一齊挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n買左機票既我地身無分文，所以成個暑假都好努力返工。因為我地可能只係黎呢個地方一次，而紐西蘭主要分為南北島，而我同廢青都好想盡行，想用呢12日睇下行到幾多得幾多。<br />\n<br />\n我地行程如下<br />\n南島HKG &gt; Auckland &gt; Christchurch &gt; Hokitika &gt; Queenstown &gt; Invercagill &gt; Bluff &gt; Oamaru &gt; Christchurch<br />\n<br />\n北島 Christchurch &gt; Auckland &gt; Matamata &gt; Waitomo &gt; Lake Taupo &gt; Lake Rotorua &gt; Auckland &gt; HKG<br />\n<br />\n住宿：<br />\n南島 AIRBNB * 6晚<br />\n北島 Camper van * 5晚<br />\n機場 1晚<br />\n<br />\n人均洗費<br />\n機票3000+1000(內陸機)<br />\n租車 1200+2000<br />\nBNB ： 1600<br />\n當地洗費（食＋入油） 5000<br />\n哈比人晚宴 1200<br />\nSKYDIVE連相，片 4000<br />\n12日Total : HKD20000 <br />\n平均一日都係大約$1700（包食住交通機票）,係當地黎講已經算玩得好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay1 香港 &gt; Auckland &gt; Christchruch<br />\n<br />\n一落機過安全檢查個到，個機場瘋狂叫我地CHECK下有無野食係我地既行李<br />\n每行兩步就有幾張POSTER 大大隻字咁寫出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身我地都幾肯定我地無帶食物過黎，但見到佢要罰成3000HKD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，又咁多提示，我同廢青決定DOUBLE CHECK多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n如果大家去既話，記得唔好帶，包括機上面既食物，杯麵都計架。<br />\n<br />\n香港時間1600 上機 飛左10個鐘 加埋時差海關，出到機場係當地時間0730左右。<br />\n原本個我地係訂左1700 JetStar 飛去Christchruch, 打算用呢10個鐘空檔出市區行下街，但最後發覺出去市區既SHUTTLE 要20NZD / head, 大家可以當1NZD = 6 HKD咁計， 最後因為覺得好唔抵，去左JETSTAR到改機票， 最後改左1100機，手續費係30NZD ／ HEAD。 <br />\n咁我地岩岩落機又係機場廢到上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又餓又累又眼訓，一上JETSTAR就訓死左，<br />\n6677覺得JETSTAR個位仲舒服過HX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾經辛苦 終於到左christchruch <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溫度大概 12度左右，本身我地著緊頹TEE 都即刻拎返D褸出黎著<br />\n<br />\n我地打電話去JUCY 叫佢地派SHUTTLE黎接我地攞車。 第一個司機叫我地去door 7到等，等左勁耐都無車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。再打多次又話係door 1, 點知原來door 1一出個位係door7 出左再行多100米咁上下，明明就係個司機講得唔清楚，搞到又餓又累既廢青就屌鳩我話唔問人又處理得唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我都好餓好累，只係個司機講得唔清楚渣嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n搞左一大輪，終於拎到租個部車。我地決定左去BNB到SETTLE好再算，因為真係好累。<br />\n渣左40分鐘車，終於到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/160906_28ffcd7dca673cb34c7519950800d2a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F160906_28ffcd7dca673cb34c7519950800d2a3.jpg&h=950aea35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢到d人都會dec 到間屋好靚好detail, 相比係香港真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地呢之前都做左reserach 知道呢到食野好貴好貴，大多數都係自己煮。<br />\n我地已經餓到唔記得自己有幾餓，所以沖個熱水涼就出發去supermarket 買野<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/161311_1f754a3ccc130b2d323c1c753ed77d48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F161311_1f754a3ccc130b2d323c1c753ed77d48.jpg&h=62016c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢間叫PAK n SAVE, 係nz黎講都算幾大，模式似costco,(有去過美國／台灣應該知）都係一個大貨倉咁咩都有， 我地第一日就買左牛扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，雞脾，意粉同，fish finger 加少少調味料。 買單個陣 一睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十樣野成600幾700蚊港紙，心諗呢間野咁貴既，都唔知D人係咪呃鳩我話呢間好。<br />\n明明好出名既 NZ安格斯 ribeye 2大塊先 80蚊港紙，再睇先知蒜頭，洋蔥都好撚貴 成10幾20蚊港紙一粒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肚餓唔理啦，返到去就交比廢青煮啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/162234_15e10a7ccc054544e2bdd2ee73318628.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F162234_15e10a7ccc054544e2bdd2ee73318628.png&h=f7f93cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大廚出馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部都好好味， 塊牛扒買個陣係有D暗紅色，唔似香港既血紅色。我地初頭以為壞左，但個HOST話係正常。 我地就照食，味道同口感都正過香港所謂既扒房多多聲，又平喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為太支力，所以食飽飽 就訓到第2朝了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb09c5b932fc3520564fac6a143a7fc3dd3eb28c","tid":402173,"uid":25286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"啪左幾多次？"},{"pid":"bd877e6c5107d3972c73dd3a3c7d230283dc5d42","tid":402173,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啪左幾多次？</blockquote><br />\n12日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11345d8b42e9ba48fd929685e3f202c0fb42405f","tid":402173,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"DAY2 Christchurch &gt; Stone Castle Hill&gt; Hokitika  (260km)<br />\n訓到8點，我地食個早餐整個lunch box再出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/155323_89ca687a7c5c0aebf2675302aa7d1634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F155323_89ca687a7c5c0aebf2675302aa7d1634.jpg&h=5f2bd1dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第一站我地去castle hill， 大約160km, 要渣2.5-3hr, 仲要瘋狂上山落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果無渣開車既巴絲真係要量力阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n經過左一番博鬥，終於到左castle hill，但我地一到就開始落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/165416_b0bbce4c85198761af3e57d6fc07032b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F165416_b0bbce4c85198761af3e57d6fc07032b.jpg&h=7d4b86f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係一大堆唔同大小形狀既石頭係個山頭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行近去睇 其實都幾壯觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好明點解會生成咁又生埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/170151_c74beff1cd34ab681fbe1754d69326ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F170151_c74beff1cd34ab681fbe1754d69326ab.jpg&h=c928332b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/170805_908ac9873af12b441c248a63f029da78.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F170805_908ac9873af12b441c248a63f029da78.JPG&h=c80c7c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/170420_bb67d24f26821e83bc133c390bb65f2d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F170420_bb67d24f26821e83bc133c390bb65f2d.JPG&h=de8e077c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前面係石，後面就係呢D雪山美景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇完呢個 原訂係去 Arthur's Pass, 但因為太大雨，廢雨又係車到訓死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我同個路牌影左張相就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/171412_44b2ae51c30b5d39c8e9ae0648002a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F171412_44b2ae51c30b5d39c8e9ae0648002a34.jpg&h=cf15462a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路上就好多呢啲山水景<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/171412_c0502abf7496ccff00ea101d6d52bc34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F171412_c0502abf7496ccff00ea101d6d52bc34.jpg&h=45d94a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地就係呢條咁靚既河邊食晏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/171903_a62e3b8edb619076d6bf6fc35d230eb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F171903_a62e3b8edb619076d6bf6fc35d230eb7.jpg&h=69345e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我地就直奔去Hokitika 既bnb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再係Hokitika 既 New World supermarket 買左ribeye 黎煮，之後又訓死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解去到NZ之前成日都好攰 好想訓，可能係凍，可能係渣車辛苦，我地都唔知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之係到訓就好爽，因為D床又大又軟又舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另帶一提，係呢到買既牛扒係鮮紅色，我地諗返起都唔知係咪第一個HOST呃我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8054c295fab75411c57f7c10c6c44f2320c5875","tid":402173,"uid":137783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"正呀"},{"pid":"b575766ac84a194d92baffb90d6f8924a8a7b1ac","tid":402173,"uid":5327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好靚"},{"pid":"89717771d446617851d20ce86a2f2f5cebe50091","tid":402173,"uid":116896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:40:40.000Z","msg":"好想俾樓主屌屎眼"},{"pid":"c0788f6b0ff40058b1e8ab32c01b6045620a045e","tid":402173,"uid":632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想俾樓主屌屎眼</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdac7e0dd432b0c60e4c9873c7e9cb06cbbb2792","tid":402173,"uid":84912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"PakNsave d 扒係差少少"},{"pid":"4828b167247d525e46d58bfa48540f2caf6fed63","tid":402173,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PakNsave d 扒係差少少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nNew world, countdown 好食好多"},{"pid":"ae900294ac76558f7dccda09b06dd79ce6d245ea","tid":402173,"uid":129836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:43:36.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"f16bdcf6f419c2c1fa8704a04a03425e1374e76f","tid":402173,"uid":3205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:24:36.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"d7d59c3c73ab6d429a672f368a8fbd076e88c07c","tid":402173,"uid":115864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:27:58.000Z","msg":"睇到你個行程12日去咁多地方，仲要南北，chur到<i